"{\"uid\": \"abcnews4.com-news-local-behind-the-badge-mppd-sro-keeps-students-safe-while-training-for-the-olympics-mount-pleasant-police-department-100-meter-hurdle-laurel-hill-primary-paris-summer-haiti-south-carolina-sc-wciv\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Now  48\\u00b0  Tue  50\\u00b0  Wed  60\\u00b0  byKaty Solt  MOUNT PLEASANT, S.C. (WCIV) -Here on News 4, we are taking you Behind the Badge, introducing you to men and women of the Lowcountry who keep us safe.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 63, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina\", \"score\": 0.9999984130094023, \"rank\": 1.586870256641254e-06, \"text\": \"S.C.\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina\"}, {\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.261365901689892e-17, \"text\": \"Lowcountry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our latest officer is always on her feet on and off the clock.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 256, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Right now, she's training to compete on the world's largest stage.\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Behind the Badge: Chester the K-9 keeps DD2 schools safe  Here on News 4, we are taking you Behind the Badge, introducing you to men and women of the Lowcountry who keep us safe.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.261365901689892e-17, \"text\": \"Lowcountry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(WCIV)  Murlern Jean has spent the last 16 years on the track.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's complex,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You are sprinting full speed and hurtling over 10 obstacles, 10 hurdles.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's what keeps me going because like every season or every day I am learning something new, something different, and I am getting better and better at it.\\\"\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When she's not training new athletes or running laps, Jean is running after the students at Laurel Hill Primary in Mt.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurel_Hill_Historic_District\", \"score\": 0.8163806429017283, \"rank\": 0.21912338040409277, \"text\": \"Laurel Hill\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurel_Hill_Historic_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurel_Hill_Historic_District\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pleasant as their school resource officer.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(The students) always want to race me,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always race them at recess.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have some kids that think they are faster than me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jean has been the SRO for the school since 2019 and says it's her chance to combine fun with safety.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SRO_Motorsports_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999040834087034, \"rank\": 9.592576332015482e-05, \"text\": \"SRO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SRO_Motorsports_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SRO_Motorsports_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I come to the students with a smile and I let them know who I am,\\\" Jean said.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I let them know I am here at the school to keep them safe, just in case if they do not know why I I am here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ialways have that mindset that you just never know,\\\" she continued.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So always be prepared.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am always having fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When she's done patrolling the halls, Jean heads to the track to pursue her other passion.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jean competed in the 2016 and 2021 Summer Olympics in the 100-meter hurdles and is now training for the Paris competition.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1757, \"end\": 1762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999963260162719, \"rank\": 3.6739973348467472e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Behind the Badge: NCPD Officer uses cancer battle to give back  \\\"Representing Haiti was pretty big for me because we have not really sent a lot of people to the Olympics,\\\" Jean said.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a big deal just to represent my country, just to be there was a huge deal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Coming into Paris, I think I will be ready,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999963260162719, \"rank\": 3.6739973348467472e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tokyo, I made it to the semifinals, so that was a huge accomplishment for me just to make it to the next round.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This go-around, I plan on making it to the finals.\\\"\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even over the summer, Jean is still inspiring her students.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Behind the Badge: K-9s of the Lowcountry  \\\"They were the ones to tell me they watched me on TV,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2378, \"end\": 2388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.261365901689892e-17, \"text\": \"Lowcountry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Carolina_Lowcountry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That melted my heart because that came on at, you know, various times.\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes six o'clock, four o'clock in the morning.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To have them sitting there watching me or waiting up looking for me made me feel very special.\\\"\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jean says the kids she chases around the playground and sits with in classes inspire her too.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just seeing everyone smile, making them happy, and hearing the little kids say, 'Thank you for keeping us safe',\\\" Jean said.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even the teachers and the faculty, they also always thank me for being here and keeping them safe.\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's just the best part, I would say.\\\"\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2025Sinclair, Inc.\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": []}]}"